title: Roadies Promo: This Girl Came Out To Her Parents On National TV
text:
Priyam Saha Feb . 23 . 2017 Ankita Mehra on Roadies Rising 
The latest Roadies promo has an aspiring contestant come out to her parents on national TV and all the gang leaders applauded her courage and decision. Check it out! 
Are you excited for deadliest season of #Roadies? Tune into MTV this Saturday, 25th Feb at 7 PM!
